com.metreeca.gate

Interface Crypto


  • public interface Crypto
    Opaque id generator.

    Manages random and hash-based opaque id generation.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static String MessageDigestDefault
      The default message digest algorithm ("SHA-1").
      static String SecureRandomDefault
      The default secure random generator algorithm ("SHA1PRNG").

    • Method Detail

      • crypto

        static Supplier<Crypto> crypto()
        Retrieves the default opaque id generator factory.
        Returns:
        the default opaque id generator factory, which creates generators based on the default secure random generator ("SHA1PRNG") and message digest ("SHA-1") algorithms

      • random

        static SecureRandom random(String algorithm)
        Creates a secure random generator instance.
        Parameters:
        algorithm - the id of the required secure random generator algorithm
        Returns:
        a new secure random generator instance based on the required algorithm
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if algorithm is null
        UnsupportedOperationException - if algorithm is not supported

        byte[] id(int length)

      • encode

        Parameters:
